get.description: Returnerar en sträng som anger om servern är uppe.

parameters.name: client_id
parameters.description: The client ID identifing the calling client. Used for analytics and authentication.

parameters.name: client_secret
parameters.description: The client seceret authenticating that the calling client is whom it say it is.

parameters.name: AF-TrackingId
parameters.description: Used to track a request beween systems. Must be created by the originating system and forwarde by all parties. The format is a guid.

parameters.name: AF-SystemId
parameters.description: Unique identifier for the calling system.

parameters.name: AF-EndUserId
parameters.description: Identifies the calling enduser as autenticated by the calling system. Should only be used for traceing not autorization.

AF-SystemId.description: Unique identifier for the responding system.

AF-ResponseTime.description: The time it took for the system to process the request in miliseconds.

AF-EndUserId.description: Identifies the calling enduser as autenticated by the calling system. Should only be used for tracing not autorization.
